  "texts": [
    "The application values of this system according to the author include intelligent identity authentication, and better data authenticity, security, and traceability.",
    "The author put forward some basic design and implementation ideas such as blockchain platform selection where he proposed to use a consortium blockchain and highlighted the main difficulty in designing which resides mainly on the data sets stored in blockchain nodes and the process of its collection and fusion.",
    "Unfortunately, no implementation is proposed.",
    "The authors in [41] presented a blockchain-enabled system for the real-time collection and management of athlete's fitness data where the blockchain is used to render the collected data streaming from IoT devices more private and secure, which are later used to enable the athletes to understand their abilities and allow coaches to handle personal training plans more effectively.",
    "Similarly, [33] proposed a blockchain-based fitness management system."
  ]
}